01:21:52,782 --> 01:21:54,032
And No. 3?

1000
01:21:54,033 --> 01:21:55,951
Declare us as the national bird.

1001
01:21:55,952 --> 01:21:58,620
Fools. You aren't birds,
but insects.

1002
01:21:58,621 --> 01:21:59,913
It's getting late.

1003
01:21:59,914 --> 01:22:01,706
Will you come along or..
- We won't.

1004
01:22:01,707 --> 01:22:04,709
If you don't come along,
I'll kill everyone.

1005
01:22:04,710 --> 01:22:07,045
Hey. Who are you?

1006
01:22:07,046 --> 01:22:09,297
You're threatening us in our area?

1007
01:22:09,298 --> 01:22:11,258
