Dengue and Chicken Gunia.

1010
01:22:15,221 --> 01:22:16,721
Did you forget that?

1011
01:22:16,722 --> 01:22:18,098
Let's show him who we are.

1012
01:22:18,099 --> 01:22:19,266
Hey, Dengue Lakshmi.
- Yes.

1013
01:22:19,267 --> 01:22:21,602
Cholera Jasmine
attack him! Go bite him.

1014
01:22:26,941 --> 01:22:29,109
Sister, he has a thick hide.

1015
01:22:29,110 --> 01:22:31,278
Condra Jasmine has
fractured her sting.

1016
01:22:31,279 --> 01:22:32,571
Is that so?

1017
01:22:32,572 --> 01:22:35,408
Go inside his mouth when he isn't looking.
- Fine.

1018
01:22:41,038 --> 01:22:44,333
Sister, Dengue Lakshmi got
an electric shock and died.

1019
01:22:45,042 --> 01:22:48,254
Hey, this seems like a new
machine like an electric badge.

1020
01:22:48,588 --> 01:22:50,005
Act that you're scared..

1021
01:22:50,006 --> 01:22:51,298
...just like we do
when we see Tortoise..

1022
01:22:51,299 --> 01:22:52,466
...and All-Out mosquito repellents.

1023
01:22:52,467 --> 01:22:53,885
We'll deal with him later.

1024
01:22:56,429 --> 01:22:58,598
You can take Rangoski.

1025
01:22:59,432 --> 01:23:00,683
Thank you.

1026
01:23:03,644 --> 01:23:05,020
Look, Sana.

1027
01:23:05,021 --> 01:23:06,981
This is the mosquito. Rangoski.

1028
01:23:07,315 --> 01:23:11,027
Rangoski, apologize to Sana.
- Sorry.

1029
01:23:11,861 --> 01:23:14,404
Don't fly around this house again.

1030
01:23:14,405 --> 01:23:16,908
Tell your friends as well.
- Yes, boss.

1031
01:23:17,283 --> 01:23:18,493
Go.

1032
01:23:20,203 --> 01:23:22,204
Now kiss me.
- Chitti.

1033
01:23:22,205 --> 01:23:23,539
Deal is a deal.

1034
01:28:43,776 --> 01:28:44,860
This way.

1035
01:28:47,071 --> 01:28:48,405
Welcome.

1036
01:28:51,909 --> 01:28:53,911
Okay, I'll call you later.

1037
01:28:56,455 --> 01:28:57,915
Hello.

1038
01:28:59,625 --> 01:29:01,460
Bora is coming with agent Shah.

1039
01:29:03,295 --> 01:29:04,839
Meet him.
