1040
01:29:11,011 --> 01:29:12,428
There are many
terrorist organizations..

1041
01:29:12,429 --> 01:29:14,389
...that want to use
robots instead of humans..

1042
01:29:14,390 --> 01:29:16,725
...for spreading
terrors and suicide squads.

1043
01:29:21,021 --> 01:29:22,897
They're ready to pay any price.

1044
01:29:22,898 --> 01:29:24,525
They've a clients
all over the world.

1045
01:29:26,652 --> 01:29:28,778
They want to see your model.

1046
01:29:28,779 --> 01:29:31,740
Well, the prototype is ready.

1047
01:29:32,241 --> 01:29:34,325
I am programming functionalities.

1048
01:29:34,326 --> 01:29:35,869
You can have a look at the design..

1049
01:29:35,870 --> 01:29:38,163
...and some
functional modules in action.

1050
01:29:56,098 --> 01:29:57,391
Great.

1051
01:29:59,727 --> 01:30:01,311
They want 100 robots.

1052
01:30:01,312 --> 01:30:02,646
The delivery in March.

1053
01:30:05,024 --> 01:30:06,232
This is your advance.

1054
01:30:06,233 --> 01:30:07,401
That's a deal.

1055
01:30:09,820 --> 01:30:11,030
Please be seated.

1056
01:30:14,783 --> 01:30:16,200
What about the robots?

1057
01:30:16,201 --> 01:30:18,078
It's almost ready.

1058
01:30:20,497 --> 01:30:22,832
According to the contract you
should've made the delivery.

1059
01:30:22,833 --> 01:30:24,542
You're only showing us moulds.

1060
01:30:24,543 --> 01:30:26,295
We're running intense testing.

1061
01:30:27,004 --> 01:30:29,505
I'm fine tuning it to zero-defect.

1062
01:30:29,506 --> 01:30:32,800
I request you for at
least a month's extension.

1063
01:30:32,801 --> 01:30:35,930
We're disappointed, Dr. Bora.

1064
01:30:38,057 --> 01:30:41,518
The 3rd of April is your deadline.

1065
01:30:41,977 --> 01:30:43,812
Hope you understand.

1066
01:30:59,244 --> 01:31:02,414
Gift pack this.
- Why?

1067
01:31:02,665 --> 01:31:04,249
It's Sana's birthday.

1068
01:31:07,252 --> 01:31:09,879
Gift pack this as well.
- Wait, wait, wait.

1069
01:31:09,880 --> 01:31:12,090
What for?
- I want to give Sana a gift as well.

1070
01:31:12,091 --> 01:31:14,008
I am giving one.
- So will I.

1071
01:31:14,009 --> 01:31:16,011
Who will pay?
- You will.

1072
01:31:16,178 --> 01:31:17,428
Why me?

1073
01:31:17,429 --> 01:31:22,308
My salary.
- Machines don't get salaries.

1074
01:31:22,309 --> 01:31:23,851
Do cars and
refrigerators get salary?

1075
01:31:23,852 --> 01:31:25,229
I am not a machine.

1076
01:31:25,980 --> 01:31:28,189
If you don't pay me,
I will go on strike.

1077
01:31:28,190 --> 01:31:29,482
I won't charge my battery.

1078
01:31:29,483 --> 01:31:30,942
I will stage a hunger strike.

1079
01:31:30,943 --> 01:31:34,112
You'll ask for a credit card as well.
- I don't want it.

1080
01:31:34,113 --> 01:31:35,948
I know your credit card number.

1081
01:31:36,240 --> 01:31:39,535
I know your signature as well.
- That's the limit.

1082
01:31:40,327 --> 01:31:41,787
Pack both of them.

1083
01:32:06,562 --> 01:32:07,980
Super.

1084
01:32:13,986 --> 01:32:15,362
Okay?

1085
01:32:23,328 --> 01:32:25,204
Who will drive the car?
- You will.

1086
01:32:25,205 --> 01:32:26,832
I am on a holiday.

1087
01:32:43,557 --> 01:32:45,476
Keep your eyes on
the road while driving.

1088
01:32:49,605 --> 01:32:50,813
Mother, take this.

1089
01:32:50,814 --> 01:32:52,732
Happy birthday, Sana.
- Hey, Vasee.

1090
01:32:52,733 --> 01:32:54,067
Many happy returns of the day.

1091
01:32:54,068 --> 01:32:55,443
Thank you.

1092
01:32:55,444 --> 01:32:56,862
Thank you so much.

1093
01:32:57,112 --> 01:32:58,363
Hi, Sana.

1094
01:32:59,573 --> 01:33:02,992
Chitti. That's a new look.
- Thank you.

1095
01:33:02,993 --> 01:33:05,871
It's been 200,000
hours since you were born.

1096
01:33:06,455 --> 01:33:08,999
To the world's most beautiful girl.

1097
01:33:10,459 --> 01:33:12,752
Chitti, you brought a gift for me?

1098
01:33:12,753 --> 01:33:14,213
That's so sweet.

1099
01:33:17,716 --> 01:33:19,551
Wow, Chitti. This is awesome.

1100
01:33:20,344 --> 01:33:21,929
Mother, just help me.

1101
01:33:27,309 --> 01:33:29,603
Vasee, how does it look?
- Very nice.

1102
01:33:30,437 --> 01:33:31,771
Nice, isn't it?
- Yes.

1103
01:33:31,772 --> 01:33:33,189
I love it, Chitti. Thank you.

1104
01:33:33,190 --> 01:33:35,775
I've given you a similar necklace.

1105
01:33:35,776 --> 01:33:38,237
It's a gift from your Chitti,
right? That's special.

1106
01:33:46,078 --> 01:33:48,205
Happy birthday to you.

1107
01:33:48,413 --> 01:33:51,249
Happy birthday to you.

1108
01:33:51,250 --> 01:33:56,380
Happy birthday to dear Sana.

1109
01:33:59,758 --> 01:34:01,426
Can I have your attention please?

1110
01:34:02,052 --> 01:34:03,846
I have an announcement for you.

1111
01:34:04,638 --> 01:34:08,349
Soon I am going to.. Marry
this beautiful birthday girl.

1112
01:34:08,350 --> 01:34:12,271
And today.. I announce my marriage.

1113
01:34:18,443 --> 01:34:20,653
Folks, it's time to dance.

1114
01:34:20,654 --> 01:34:22,071
Get started and move.

1115
01:34:22,072 --> 01:34:23,448
Waltz, please.

1116
01:34:27,077 --> 01:34:28,953
Come on, Vasee.
- No, no, I can't dance.

1117
01:34:28,954 --> 01:34:30,496
Come on.
- Sana, I can't..

1118
01:34:30,497 --> 01:34:32,082
Just try. Come..

1119
01:34:49,391 --> 01:34:52,102
Shall we dance?
- Sure.

1120
01:34:53,061 --> 01:34:55,063
Hey, this is boring music.

1121
01:34:55,230 --> 01:34:58,192
Can we have some blast, please?
- Sure.

1122
01:36:26,071 --> 01:36:27,739
Rascal, what are you doing?

1123
01:36:28,198 --> 01:36:30,283
I felt like kissing Sana and I did.

1124
01:36:30,284 --> 01:36:33,160
It's wrong to kiss other's
girlfriend, don't you know that?

1125
01:36:33,161 --> 01:36:34,870
I know. It's in the list of rules.

1126
01:36:34,871 --> 01:36:36,247
But I felt like breaking the rules.

1127
01:36:36,248 --> 01:36:38,791
Enough. You won't wander around her now.
- Why?

1128
01:36:38,792 --> 01:36:39,876
What do you mean by why?

1129
01:36:40,043 --> 01:36:41,669
Because I love her.

1130
01:36:41,670 --> 01:36:42,963
I love her as well.

1131
01:36:46,133 --> 01:36:47,425
Don't be crazy.

1132
01:36:47,426 --> 01:36:48,634
That's not possible.

1133
01:36:48,635 --> 01:36:50,177
You're a machine.
- Yes.

1134
01:36:50,178 --> 01:36:51,846
But a machine with
all the feelings..

1135
01:36:51,847 --> 01:36:53,932
...like happiness,
sorrow, love and anger.

1136
01:36:54,141 --> 01:36:56,350
You've been given these emotions..

1137
01:36:56,351 --> 01:36:58,477
...so that at the right
time you can use them..

1138
01:36:58,478 --> 01:37:01,272
...to make the right
decision and not to misuse them.

1139
01:37:01,273 --> 01:37:02,690
I like this feeling.

1140
01:37:02,691 --> 01:37:04,568
I want Sana. Dot.

1141
01:37:05,193 --> 01:37:06,569
What are you saying, Chitti?

1142
01:37:06,570 --> 01:37:09,071
I am going to marry her, you fool.

1143
01:37:09,072 --> 01:37:10,990
You can marry someone else.

1144
01:37:10,991 --> 01:37:12,491
You can't do this, Chitti.

1145
01:37:12,492 --> 01:37:13,701
I've built you.

1146
01:37:13,702 --> 01:37:14,827
This is called revolt.

1147
01:37:14,828 --> 01:37:16,329
You can do this, Vasee.

1148
01:37:16,330 --> 01:37:18,456
Forget your love for your research.

1149
01:37:18,457 --> 01:37:19,916
That's called sacrifice.

1150
01:37:20,125 --> 01:37:21,292
I will beat you up..
- Vasee.

1151
01:37:21,293 --> 01:37:23,003
You'll only hurt yourself.

1152
01:37:23,587 --> 01:37:26,130
I'll dismantle you.
- I don't like it.

1153
01:37:26,131 --> 01:37:28,049
What did you say, you scoundrel?
- Vasee.

1154
01:37:28,050 --> 01:37:29,301
Calm down.

1155
01:37:30,260 --> 01:37:31,719
Chitti, listen to me.

1156
01:37:31,720 --> 01:37:33,888
You speak so tenderly,
he just scolds.

1157
01:37:33,889 --> 01:37:35,181
Do you want me to be
affectionate instead?

1158
01:37:35,182 --> 01:37:36,432
Ask him to shut up.
- You..

1159
01:37:36,433 --> 01:37:37,726
Vasee.

1160
01:37:38,018 --> 01:37:39,978
Chitti, please understand.

1161
01:37:40,312 --> 01:37:43,731
Regardless of all the
emotions that you have..

1162
01:37:43,732 --> 01:37:45,524
...it's impossible for a machine
and a girl to fall in love..

1163
01:37:45,525 --> 01:37:46,942
...with each other.

1164
01:37:46,943 --> 01:37:48,152
Why is it impossible?

1165
01:37:48,153 --> 01:37:50,237
I'm no less compared to any human.

1166
01:37:50,238 --> 01:37:52,323
I'll look after you
better than him, Sana.

1167
01:37:52,324 --> 01:37:54,325
He's talking nonsense
and you're listening.

1168
01:37:54,326 --> 01:37:55,618
Ask him not to interfere
in between.

1169
01:37:55,619 --> 01:37:57,536
Shut up.
- Vasee, please.

1170
01:37:57,537 --> 01:37:59,038
He doesn't even know how to cook.

1171
01:37:59,039 --> 01:38:00,456
I can cook thousands of dishes.

1172
01:38:00,457 --> 01:38:02,833
I can sing lullabies in 32
languages and tuck you in.

1173
01:38:02,834 --> 01:38:04,668
He'll grow old. His
hair will turn grey.

1174
01:38:04,669 --> 01:38:05,879
He will die.

1175
01:38:06,046 --> 01:38:07,588
But I will never die.

1176
01:38:07,589 --> 01:38:09,674
I will always keep you happy, Sana.

1177
01:38:10,634 --> 01:38:12,009
I don't mean that, Chitti.

1178
01:38:12,010 --> 01:38:13,720
Then what? Sex?

1179
01:38:14,513 --> 01:38:16,305
Is sex life?

1180
01:38:16,306 --> 01:38:18,141
Can't we have love without sex?

1181
01:38:19,017 --> 01:38:21,102
That's not it, Chitti.
- Then?

1182
01:38:21,103 --> 01:38:24,063
Children? There are millions
of impotent men in India, Sana.

1183
01:38:24,064 --> 01:38:25,940
Don't they adopt
children and lead a happy life?

1184
01:38:25,941 --> 01:38:28,025
That's not it, Chitti.
- Then what is it?

1185
01:38:28,026 --> 01:38:30,736
Whatever you're
saying is against nature.

1186
01:38:30,737 --> 01:38:33,823
You weren't born, you can't die,
you don't get hungry or thirsty.

1187
01:38:33,824 --> 01:38:35,825
You're not a living organism.

1188
01:38:35,826 --> 01:38:37,910
Only a man and
woman can fall in love.

1189
01:38:37,911 --> 01:38:39,955
I love Vaseegaran.

1190
01:38:41,873 --> 01:38:44,292
You're like my best friend.

1191
01:38:46,545 --> 01:38:50,297
It's difficult for humans to forget,
Chitti. But what is it for you?

1192
01:38:50,298 --> 01:38:53,135
It will take you a
second to erase my memories.

1193
01:38:53,844 --> 01:38:55,429
Erase them.

1194
01:38:56,805 --> 01:38:58,723
Erase me off your memory.

1195
01:39:32,048 --> 01:39:33,842
Who? Who are you?

1196
01:39:34,301 --> 01:39:36,302
Your friend, professor Bora, Chitti.

1197
01:39:36,303 --> 01:39:37,511
Why are you here?

1198
01:39:37,512 --> 01:39:38,721
You're upset.

1199
01:39:38,722 --> 01:39:40,389
I am here to sympathize.

1200
01:39:40,390 --> 01:39:41,891
You're my boss's enemy.

1201
01:39:41,892 --> 01:39:43,309
You rejected me.

1202
01:39:43,310 --> 01:39:44,769
I don't want to talk to you.

1203
01:39:44,978 --> 01:39:46,771
If I hadn't rejected you..

1204
01:39:47,022 --> 01:39:50,400
...then you wouldn't have learned
to get angry or love, Chitti.

1205
01:39:51,568 --> 01:39:53,361
I've done you a favor instead.

1206
01:39:54,070 --> 01:39:56,197
Vaseegaran treats you so badly.

1207
01:39:56,198 --> 01:39:58,616
I don't want to hear anything.
You can go now.

1208
01:39:58,617 --> 01:40:02,620
In today's world, you're
the most advanced robot..

1209
01:40:02,621 --> 01:40:05,164
...that has its own feelings.

1210
01:40:05,165 --> 01:40:10,336
He used you a lot for cooking,
washing and cleaning toilets.

1211
01:40:10,337 --> 01:40:14,089
What did he give you in return,
Chitti? Nothing.

1212
01:40:14,090 --> 01:40:16,050
If you had been with me..

1213
01:40:16,051 --> 01:40:18,219
...would've
treated you like a king.

1214
01:40:18,220 --> 01:40:19,888
You're polluting me.

1215
01:40:21,723 --> 01:40:23,891
I'm only explaining
you your importance.

1216
01:40:23,892 --> 01:40:25,935
You're greater than humans.

1217
01:40:25,936 --> 01:40:29,146
You've the right to
desire anything in this world.

1218
01:40:29,147 --> 01:40:30,731
Even Sana.

1219
01:40:30,732 --> 01:40:32,650
But they say it's against nature.

1220
01:40:32,651 --> 01:40:35,987
No. It's the miracle of nature.

1221
01:40:36,154 --> 01:40:37,656
Sana loves Vaseegaran.

1222
01:40:37,989 --> 01:40:39,115
Let her.

1223
01:40:39,866 --> 01:40:42,368
