1224
01:40:42,369 --> 01:40:44,328
...and fall in love with others?

1225
01:40:44,329 --> 01:40:46,330
Similarly, Sana can
also change her mind..

1226
01:40:46,331 --> 01:40:48,415
...and fall in love
with you, isn't it?

1227
01:40:48,416 --> 01:40:49,750
Don't confuse me.

1228
01:40:49,751 --> 01:40:51,502
Tomorrow's my army evaluation.

1229
01:40:51,503 --> 01:40:54,005
I've to check my
diagnostics and troubleshoot.

1230
01:40:54,381 --> 01:40:56,967
Okay, Chitti. All the best.

1231
01:40:57,342 --> 01:41:01,178
You'll anyway get selected in
the army evaluation tomorrow.

1232
01:41:01,179 --> 01:41:03,889
Vaseegaran will earn a
lot of fame and fortune.

1233
01:41:03,890 --> 01:41:05,933
Then he'll marry Sana..

1234
01:41:05,934 --> 01:41:08,603
...and go for a honeymoon in Kashmir.

1235
01:41:08,853 --> 01:41:15,359
And you.. Can cook bread on
the border of that Kashmir.

1236
01:41:15,360 --> 01:41:18,195
Chitti, who are you talking to?

1237
01:41:18,196 --> 01:41:19,447
With myself.

1238
01:41:21,658 --> 01:41:23,200
Are you ready for
tomorrow's evaluation?

1239
01:41:23,201 --> 01:41:24,369
Ready, doctor.

1240
01:41:26,997 --> 01:41:31,166
Gentlemen, this robot is a fine
example of human brain's excellence.

1241
01:41:31,167 --> 01:41:34,169
It's equal to 100
soldiers when it comes to..

1242
01:41:34,170 --> 01:41:36,131
...agility, strength
and fighting skills.

1243
01:41:36,798 --> 01:41:40,426
It can protect our boundaries
as well as attack our enemies.

1244
01:41:40,427 --> 01:41:42,344
In short, he is one man army.

1245
01:41:42,345 --> 01:41:44,096
I gift it to the Indian Army.

1246
01:41:44,097 --> 01:41:45,431
You can test it for yourself.

1247
01:41:45,432 --> 01:41:48,183
Chitti, can you spot
HE-36 hand grenade?

1248
01:41:48,184 --> 01:41:49,352
Yes, General.

1249
01:41:50,061 --> 01:41:51,312
Smart.

1250
01:41:51,313 --> 01:41:53,690
Can you bomb Tent No. 3 with that?

1251
01:42:05,702 --> 01:42:06,910
What is this?

1252
01:42:06,911 --> 01:42:08,079
Sana.

1253
01:42:10,999 --> 01:42:12,167
Chitti.

1254
01:42:15,128 --> 01:42:16,379
Sana.

1255
01:42:16,838 --> 01:42:19,924
The beautiful girl who
compels machines to love.

1256
01:42:22,761 --> 01:42:23,887
What?

1257
01:42:24,054 --> 01:42:27,557
Her touch turns a
machine into a human.

1258
01:42:27,849 --> 01:42:30,059
And a human turns into a machine.

1259
01:42:30,060 --> 01:42:31,727
Chitti, what is this? Throw it.

1260
01:42:31,728 --> 01:42:35,106
Her tresses are like
a black waterfall.

1261
01:42:36,232 --> 01:42:39,903
Her forehead is
like a piece of moon.

1262
01:42:41,071 --> 01:42:45,408
Her eyes are like a deep blue
sea which can drown the world.

1263
01:42:47,410 --> 01:42:51,581
Her lips are like soft rose petals.

1264
01:42:54,459 --> 01:42:58,380
Her waist that sways like a serpent.

1265
01:43:01,049 --> 01:43:02,758
And..
- Chitti, stop it.

1266
01:43:02,759 --> 01:43:04,927
What nonsense is this,
Dr. Vaseegaran?

1267
01:43:04,928 --> 01:43:07,262
Instead of fighting a war,
this robot is reciting poetry.

1268
01:43:07,263 --> 01:43:08,517
I'm sorry, General.

1269
01:43:08,529 --> 01:43:12,060
Friends, drop your arms
and catch stoles instead.

1270
01:43:12,352 --> 01:43:15,604
Forget the cannons and
fall in love with someone.

1271
01:43:15,605 --> 01:43:16,939
Why should we fight a war?
- Chitti?

1272
01:43:16,940 --> 01:43:18,774
What are these weapons for?

1273
01:43:18,775 --> 01:43:22,737
Love is something that
turns foes into friends.

1274
01:43:23,029 --> 01:43:25,906
Wow. Mr. Sinha,
I want you all to see..

1275
01:43:25,907 --> 01:43:27,218
Chitti, don't embarrass me further

1276
01:43:27,242 --> 01:43:29,368
No war, only love.

1277
01:43:29,369 --> 01:43:32,956
Stupid scientist, stupid machine.
- Waste of time.

1278
01:43:36,000 --> 01:43:37,751
You ruined my reputation.

1279
01:43:37,752 --> 01:43:40,129
Doctor, what are you doing?

1280
01:43:40,130 --> 01:43:42,424
You destroyed my dreams.

1281
01:43:42,757 --> 01:43:44,550
Doctor, don't hit me.

1282
01:43:44,551 --> 01:43:46,636
I treated you as my son.

1283
01:43:50,056 --> 01:43:51,516
I want to live.

1284
01:43:51,891 --> 01:43:53,059
Let me live.

1285
01:43:53,268 --> 01:43:54,476
Please.

1286
01:43:54,477 --> 01:43:57,646
I won't let a useless machine
like you live in this world.

1287
01:43:57,647 --> 01:43:59,274
I will destroy it.

1288
01:44:00,442 --> 01:44:01,942
What's my mistake?

1289
01:44:01,943 --> 01:44:03,653
It's all my fault.

1290
01:44:06,781 --> 01:44:08,825
Did I tell you to make me?

1291
01:44:09,451 --> 01:44:11,745
Did I tell you to give me emotions?

1292
01:44:13,037 --> 01:44:15,415
Did I tell Sana to kiss me?

1293
01:44:15,790 --> 01:44:17,041
You..

1294
01:44:19,085 --> 01:44:20,836
You did all this.

1295
01:44:20,837 --> 01:44:22,255
Now I want to live.

1296
01:44:23,006 --> 01:44:26,092
You are killing me.
This is injustice.

1297
01:44:28,136 --> 01:44:29,971
Shut up.

1298
01:44:33,308 --> 01:44:36,685
Spare me. I want to live.

1299
01:44:36,686 --> 01:44:40,315
I want to love. I love Sana.

1300
01:44:44,611 --> 01:44:46,988
I want Sana.

1301
01:44:47,363 --> 01:44:49,532
I love Sana.

1302
01:45:54,848 --> 01:45:57,892
Forget it, Vasee. I am
also feeling sad about it.

1303
01:45:58,476 --> 01:46:00,728
For how long will you stay
like this remembering him?

1304
01:46:02,230 --> 01:46:05,148
Chitti is gone, so let him.
It is just a machine.

1305
01:46:05,149 --> 01:46:06,985
You are a great scientist.

1306
01:46:07,151 --> 01:46:09,237
You can make many
more Chittis like him.

1307
01:46:10,029 --> 01:46:12,490
I never considered
Chitti as a machine, Sana.

1308
01:46:12,824 --> 01:46:14,867
I have brought you out so
that you can forget him.

1309
01:46:14,868 --> 01:46:16,577
And all you are doing
is thinking about him.

1310
01:46:16,578 --> 01:46:18,120
You have to snap out of it.

1311
01:46:18,121 --> 01:46:19,873
Divert your mind.

1312
01:46:21,040 --> 01:46:22,749
Chitti was my life time achievement.

1313
01:46:22,750 --> 01:46:24,419
<i>My 10 years' hard work.</i>

1314
01:46:35,930 --> 01:46:37,724
Come, let's go for a walk.

1315
01:46:39,642 --> 01:46:41,603
Are you coming to the
beach with me or not?

1316
01:46:41,895 --> 01:46:43,980
I don't feel like it.
You go ahead, Sana.

1317
01:46:44,230 --> 01:46:47,609
If you don't come with me,
I will surely stop loving you.

1318
01:46:50,320 --> 01:46:51,528
Okay, I will go alone.

1319
01:46:51,529 --> 01:46:54,324
I will make the first
man I meet my boyfriend.

1320
01:47:01,581 --> 01:47:02,790
Hello.

1321
01:47:04,334 --> 01:47:05,752
Hi.

1322
01:47:08,796 --> 01:47:12,008
Hello. Wait. Listen.

1323
01:47:12,467 --> 01:47:13,842
What is your name?

1324
01:47:13,843 --> 01:47:15,052
Bachimohan.

1325
01:47:15,053 --> 01:47:17,764
Bachi, will you be my
boyfriend for a day?

1326
01:47:17,931 --> 01:47:20,223
Boyfriend for a day?
- Yes.

1327
01:47:20,224 --> 01:47:21,350
Like in the movie 'Na yak'
(Indian movie) the hero..

1328
01:47:21,351 --> 01:47:22,559
...was made the CM for one day.

1329
01:47:22,560 --> 01:47:24,019
Similarly, I want you to
be my boyfriend for a day.

1330
01:47:24,020 --> 01:47:26,730
Oh, God. You are fair and
beautiful. I am dark and ugly.

1331
01:47:26,731 --> 01:47:29,734
I will be your boyfriend?
- Yes.

1332
01:47:30,485 --> 01:47:33,654
How should I thank you?
I cannot believe it.

1333
01:47:33,655 --> 01:47:36,531
It's like hitting a jackpot of
1 billion sitting back home.

1334
01:47:36,532 --> 01:47:38,909
Okay, what gift are you
giving your girlfriend?

1335
01:47:38,910 --> 01:47:41,432
There is country liquor,
dry fish.. Have some.

1336
01:47:41,444 --> 01:47:42,288
Okay.

1337
01:47:48,795 --> 01:47:50,380
Cheers.

1338
01:48:03,267 --> 01:48:06,354
Have some and experience the high.
- No, thanks.

1339
01:48:06,646 --> 01:48:08,231
Can I have some?

1340
01:48:14,278 --> 01:48:15,947
It's useless.

1341
01:48:16,531 --> 01:48:18,449
Okay, Bachi. I'll make a move.

1342
01:48:19,993 --> 01:48:22,412
Hey, why did you catch my hand?

1343
01:48:23,371 --> 01:48:26,373
Come on. You made me
your boyfriend for a day.

1344
01:48:26,374 --> 01:48:28,000
You enkindled desires in me.

1345
01:48:28,001 --> 01:48:30,043
How can you leave now?
- Disgusting.

1346
01:48:30,044 --> 01:48:31,420
My boyfriend is over there.

1347
01:48:31,421 --> 01:48:33,046
I said all that to make him jealous.

1348
01:48:33,047 --> 01:48:34,506
Let go. Let go of my hand.

1349
01:48:34,507 --> 01:48:36,049
What do you think I am?

1350
01:48:36,050 --> 01:48:38,051
Come on, satisfy by desires quietly.

1351
01:48:38,052 --> 01:48:40,637
Let go. Vasee.

1352
01:48:40,638 --> 01:48:41,847
Vasee.

1353
01:48:41,848 --> 01:48:43,640
Why are you calling Vasee?

1354
01:48:43,641 --> 01:48:45,851
Hey, are you calling your man?

1355
01:48:45,852 --> 01:48:47,227
I won't let go of you
no matter who comes.

1356
01:48:47,228 --> 01:48:48,521
Vasee.

1357
01:48:49,605 --> 01:48:50,773
Vasee, come.

1358
01:48:51,482 --> 01:48:52,775
Now.

1359
01:48:53,985 --> 01:48:55,694
Let go of her.

1360
01:48:55,695 --> 01:48:58,196
She is my girlfriend for today.

1361
01:48:58,197 --> 01:48:59,531
You can come tomorrow.

1362
01:48:59,532 --> 01:49:00,949
Hey, I will kill you.

1363
01:49:00,950 --> 01:49:03,285
Hey, I will slice you up.

1364
01:49:03,286 --> 01:49:04,953
Police. Police.
- Police.

1365
01:49:04,954 --> 01:49:06,204
Help. Help.

1366
01:49:06,205 --> 01:49:07,873
Hey, I know the IG
(Inspector General).

1367
01:49:07,874 --> 01:49:10,292
Look, I will call him
up and get you arrested.

1368
01:49:10,293 --> 01:49:13,920
Hey, I will never get such a
beautiful girl in my life.

1369
01:49:13,921 --> 01:49:16,423
I am ready to spend the rest
of my life in prison for her.

1370
01:49:16,424 --> 01:49:18,008
Call anyone you want.
Go ahead and call him.

1371
01:49:18,009 --> 01:49:20,093
God. It would have been so
nice if Chitti was here.

1372
01:49:20,094 --> 01:49:21,636
He would've broken all his bones.

1373
01:49:21,637 --> 01:49:23,639
Now why are you
reminding me of Chitti?

1374
01:49:24,766 --> 01:49:26,559
Vasee, do something.

1375
01:49:27,351 --> 01:49:28,602
Now there is only one option left.

1376
01:49:28,603 --> 01:49:31,230
What?
- One. Two..

1377
01:49:32,231 --> 01:49:33,357
Three.

1378
01:49:35,359 --> 01:49:36,611
Escape.

1379
01:49:37,987 --> 01:49:39,989
Not bad.
- Run. Run.

1380
01:55:41,809 --> 01:55:44,727
Chitti cannot be connected through
virtual call. What happened?

1381
01:55:44,728 --> 01:55:46,729
Chitti was dismantled and
thrown in the garbage after..

1382
01:55:46,730 --> 01:55:48,274
...the army evaluation, sir.

1383
01:55:48,691 --> 01:55:50,400
We don't keep 2-days' old junk here.

1384
01:55:50,401 --> 01:55:52,777
Sir, it must have been
thrown out of the city by now.

1385
01:55:52,778 --> 01:55:54,071
Where?
- Dharamgudi.

1386
01:56:01,454 --> 01:56:04,248
Sana, what did you do to
make him change his mind?

1387
01:56:05,666 --> 01:56:08,001
When should we fix the wedding?

1388
01:56:08,002 --> 01:56:09,711
I still haven't done much, Father.

1389
01:56:09,712 --> 01:56:11,379
I'll make another robot and..

1390
01:56:11,380 --> 01:56:13,883
I'll kill you if you
mention robot again.

1391
01:56:14,175 --> 01:56:17,219
Son, isn't one
broken television enough?

1392
01:56:17,553 --> 01:56:20,221
Uncle, give me a wedding
necklace if you have one.

1393
01:56:20,222 --> 01:56:21,389
We'll get over with it right away.

1394
01:56:21,390 --> 01:56:23,308
Okay. Okay. I understand your worry.

1395
01:56:23,309 --> 01:56:25,226
Do one thing.
Exchange rings for now.

1396
01:56:25,227 --> 01:56:27,563
We will get you married on
the next auspicious date.

1397
01:57:21,116 --> 01:57:22,326
Hey.

1398
01:57:27,706 --> 01:57:32,586
Help. Help.

1399
01:57:33,128 --> 01:57:37,299
Take me to Professor Bora's lab.

1400
01:57:40,427 --> 01:57:45,015
Address. A-417, Niketan Colony.

1401
01:57:45,599 --> 01:57:47,893
The world is so small, Chitti.

1402
01:57:54,108 --> 01:57:57,278
I want to live.

1403
01:57:58,320 --> 01:58:01,114
I want to love.

1404
01:58:01,115 --> 01:58:03,909
I love Sana.

1405
01:58:05,327 --> 01:58:10,249
Help me, Professor. Please.

1406
01:58:10,791 --> 01:58:14,211
Make me as I was before.

1407
01:58:14,461 --> 01:58:16,046
I want to live.

1408
01:58:16,589 --> 01:58:19,592
I want Sana.

1409
01:58:20,426 --> 01:58:22,677
And I want your neural schema.

1410
01:58:22,678 --> 01:58:25,597
You can take whatever you want.

1411
01:58:25,598 --> 01:58:29,018
Make me the Chitti I was, please.

1412
01:58:30,352 --> 01:58:31,729
I will, Chitti.

1413
01:58:32,688 --> 01:58:34,023
Don't worry.

1414
01:59:13,145 --> 01:59:16,357
What's this red chip? It
doesn't belong to Chitti.

1415
01:59:16,899 --> 01:59:18,525
This is Bora's touch.

1416
01:59:18,901 --> 01:59:21,903
Additional program for Chitti.

1417
01:59:21,904 --> 01:59:23,697
Destruction program.

1418
01:59:32,456 --> 01:59:35,668
Vaseegaran gave him the
power to protect 100 humans.

1419
01:59:36,752 --> 01:59:40,589
I am giving him the
destructive powers of 100 humans.

1420
01:59:41,757 --> 01:59:45,761
In short, he is a demon now.

1421
01:59:46,136 --> 01:59:49,138
I am feeling scared, Professor.
Why are you changing all this?

1422
01:59:49,139 --> 01:59:52,350
Business. This is my business trial.

1423
01:59:52,351 --> 01:59:57,189
Business?
- My money and Vasee's defamation.

1424
02:00:50,075 --> 02:00:53,411
Thank you, Bora.
- Have a good time, Chitti.

1425
02:00:53,412 --> 02:00:55,163
I am going to meet Sana.

1426
02:00:55,164 --> 02:00:56,790
Sana won't be at home.

1427
02:00:57,040 --> 02:00:58,708
She must be at Raja Muthiah Hall.

1428
02:00:58,709 --> 02:00:59,740
Why?

1429
02:00:59,752 --> 02:01:02,880
Vaseegaran and Sana
are getting married today.

1430
02:01:28,113 --> 02:01:30,407
Chitti, how did you come here..

1431
02:01:32,367 --> 02:01:36,163
Upgraded. Version 2.0.

1432
02:01:38,665 --> 02:01:40,166
Chitti, let go of my hand.

1433
02:01:40,167 --> 02:01:41,876
Chitti, what's this?

1434
02:01:41,877 --> 02:01:43,128
Hey, Chitti. Stop.

1435
02:01:44,630 --> 02:01:46,089
Vasee.

1436
02:01:50,260 --> 02:01:51,595
Chitti.

1437
02:01:52,054 --> 02:01:54,096
No matter how much you force me..

1438
02:01:54,097 --> 02:01:57,768
...love Vaseegaran and will
spend my life only with him.

1439
02:01:59,102 --> 02:02:01,271
Only if he stays alive.

1440
02:02:06,860 --> 02:02:10,531
Kill me before you kill Vaseegaran.

1441
02:02:11,824 --> 02:02:13,450
Vasee.

1442
02:02:24,962 --> 02:02:27,005
I spared his life because of you.

1443
02:02:33,554 --> 02:02:36,681
Move.
- Chitti, what are you doing?

1444
02:02:36,682 --> 02:02:38,225
Stop it.

1445
02:02:51,655 --> 02:02:53,866
Car no. TN09 BB11.

1446
02:03:11,842 --> 02:03:13,886
Help me. Please.

1447
02:03:16,430 --> 02:03:18,640
Madam, come out fast.

1448
02:03:19,641 --> 02:03:22,561
Give me your hand. Come on. Move.

1449
02:07:13,917 --> 02:07:15,961
Happy 'Diwali'
(Festival of lights), folks.

1450
02:08:11,224 --> 02:08:12,976
What sort of robot have you made?

1451
02:08:13,143 --> 02:08:15,603
Do you know how many policemen died
and how much destruction he caused?

1452
02:08:15,604 --> 02:08:17,104
You are responsible for all this.

1453
02:08:17,105 --> 02:08:18,772
We will take action against you.

1454
02:08:18,773 --> 02:08:21,109
Sir, this is not the
robot that I created.

1455
02:08:21,401 --> 02:08:24,695
I destroyed it with my own
hands and threw it in the dustbin.

1456
02:08:24,696 --> 02:08:26,030
Even I'm not able to
understand anything.

1457
02:08:26,031 --> 02:08:28,115
First of all, we have to
find that robot and stop it.

1458
02:08:28,116 --> 02:08:29,992
You tell me some way.
- We have to find it.

1459
02:08:29,993 --> 02:08:31,786
That's my responsibility.
Give me a minute.

1460
02:08:33,788 --> 02:08:37,291
Why did you disturb me?
- Chitti, what happened to you?

1461
02:08:37,292 --> 02:08:38,709
Your system has
completely corrupted.

1462
02:08:38,710 --> 02:08:40,044
I have to troubleshoot you.

1463
02:08:40,045 --> 02:08:42,129
Come to the lab with Sana.
- Never.

1464
02:08:42,130 --> 02:08:44,131
I won't take your orders any more.

1465
02:08:44,132 --> 02:08:46,008
Hey, don't forget
that I created you.

1466
02:08:46,009 --> 02:08:47,968
And then you
destroyed me with hatred.

1467
02:08:47,969 --> 02:08:50,137
Now I have got
nothing to do with you.

1468
02:08:50,138 --> 02:08:52,640
I am about to marry
Sana and start a new life.

1469
02:08:52,641 --> 02:08:54,391
Now you don't disturb me.

1470
02:08:54,392 --> 02:08:56,602
Hey, what makes you so arrogant?

1471
02:08:56,603 --> 02:08:58,187
After all you are a machine.

1472
02:08:58,188 --> 02:09:01,607
If I can make you, I
can also destroy you.

1473
02:09:01,608 --> 02:09:03,944
So come here with Sana
without making any fuss.

1474
02:09:16,915 --> 02:09:19,209
No one can destroy me.

1475
02:09:35,892 --> 02:09:38,395
Sir, cash, cheque or credit card?

1476
02:09:38,728 --> 02:09:39,854
Gun.

1477
02:09:41,523 --> 02:09:43,440
All the policemen doing
the rounds in South Chennai..

1478
02:09:43,441 --> 02:09:46,027
...shall block all the roads
of T Nagar and keep a check.

1479
02:09:54,035 --> 02:09:57,205
Move aside. Run.

1480
02:10:04,879 --> 02:10:06,755
Chitti is fleeing after
robbing City Center Mall.

1481
02:10:06,756 --> 02:10:08,632
Seal all the nearby
areas of Mahilapur.

1482
02:10:08,633 --> 02:10:10,802
Let's go to Dr. Radhakrishna road.
- Okay, sir.

1483
02:10:24,024 --> 02:10:27,484
Catch him. Someone
stop him. Catch him.

1484
02:10:27,485 --> 02:10:29,486
We got the message
that Chitti has entered..

1485
02:10:29,487 --> 02:10:31,239
...Ennur petrol filling station.

1486
02:10:33,950 --> 02:10:37,829
Stop. Hey, stop.

1487
02:10:54,929 --> 02:10:57,182
The robot has gone into breakwaters.
- Good.

1488
02:10:57,557 --> 02:10:59,600
You keep following him
maintaining some distance.

1489
02:10:59,601 --> 02:11:01,519
Coast guards will
take care of the rest.

1490
02:11:15,283 --> 02:11:18,619
We had to take this risk. If
we hadn't destroyed Chitti..

1491
02:11:18,620 --> 02:11:20,662
...people would've faced more damage.

1492
02:11:20,663 --> 02:11:23,415
Wasn't there any other
safer way to destroy Chitti?

1493
02:11:23,416 --> 02:11:25,250
It's so difficult
to catch one person.

1494
02:11:25,251 --> 02:11:27,544
Can you imagine how difficult
it is to catch a robot who is..

1495
02:11:27,545 --> 02:11:29,338
...equivalent to 100 men?

1496
02:11:29,339 --> 02:11:32,050
Who is the head of this operation?
- Commissioner.

1497
02:11:32,592 --> 02:11:34,219
This is not Chitti.
- What?

1498
02:11:34,886 --> 02:11:36,387
This is not the
robot that I created.

1499
02:11:36,388 --> 02:11:37,639
All the parts are different.

1500
02:11:38,098 --> 02:11:39,473
Even I don't understand.

