02:46:14,255 --> 02:46:17,716
This robot can become
an enemy of mankind..

1748
02:46:17,717 --> 02:46:19,926
...due to its limitless
power and intelligence.

1749
02:46:19,927 --> 02:46:22,053
And we can't overlook the danger..

1750
02:46:22,054 --> 02:46:24,890
...of it being used wrongly either.

1751
02:46:24,891 --> 02:46:28,978
An advanced robot like him
may be useful in the future.

1752
02:46:29,228 --> 02:46:33,106
But we don't need
it in today's life.

1753
02:46:33,107 --> 02:46:37,278
That's why the court
bans this robot forever.

1754
02:46:44,160 --> 02:46:48,371
The court orders to
dismantle every part of this robot..

1755
02:46:48,372 --> 02:46:50,874
...in the presence of
the district magistrate..

1756
02:46:50,875 --> 02:46:54,212
...and police
commissioner and inform the court.

1757
02:46:54,629 --> 02:46:56,506
Dismantle it.

1758
02:47:09,936 --> 02:47:11,854
You need any help, doctor?

1759
02:47:14,815 --> 02:47:17,902
Dismantle yourself, Chitti.
- Sure, doctor.

1760
02:47:25,535 --> 02:47:27,411
Shiva, Ravi.

1761
02:47:27,912 --> 02:47:30,873
You said that you've a
special thing that I don't.

1762
02:47:31,082 --> 02:47:33,417
See how many problems it created?

1763
02:47:36,921 --> 02:47:38,965
I mean feelings.

1764
02:47:41,968 --> 02:47:43,135
Don't cry.

1765
02:47:43,511 --> 02:47:45,513
Sister Lata. How is your son now?

1766
02:47:46,180 --> 02:47:48,015
I have named him after you, Chitti.

1767
02:47:49,600 --> 02:47:51,226
Mother gave me that name.

1768
02:47:51,227 --> 02:47:52,727
Educate him a lot.

1769
02:47:52,728 --> 02:47:55,398
Robotics. There's a
huge scope in future.

1770
02:47:59,151 --> 02:48:03,739
Professor Bora, just like you
installed a red chip in me..

1771
02:48:03,948 --> 02:48:08,618
...similarly every human carries
such red chips of lies, envy..

1772
02:48:08,619 --> 02:48:11,330
...deceit and
dishonesty in his heart.

1773
02:48:11,747 --> 02:48:14,709
Thankfully I am not human.

1774
02:48:15,334 --> 02:48:18,462
Otherwise I could've never got
rid of it even if I wanted to.

1775
02:48:21,424 --> 02:48:23,843
I've tormented you a lot.

1776
02:48:24,218 --> 02:48:26,470
I am extremely sorry, Sana.

1777
02:48:27,346 --> 02:48:30,516
Hey, why are you all so upset?

1778
02:48:30,850 --> 02:48:32,852
Let me tell you a joke.

1779
02:48:33,227 --> 02:48:35,980
It's said that love
makes a person lose his head.

1780
02:48:37,064 --> 02:48:38,273
Look.

1781
02:48:38,274 --> 02:48:39,984
It's the same with me.

1782
02:48:42,653 --> 02:48:45,197
I am going to miss you, Sana.

1783
02:48:45,489 --> 02:48:46,782
Not a boyfriend.

1784
02:48:47,867 --> 02:48:49,493
As a toy-friend.

1785
02:48:52,580 --> 02:48:55,958
Doctor, you're my God.

1786
02:48:56,334 --> 02:48:58,251
I betrayed you.

1787
02:48:58,252 --> 02:49:00,003
It was my mistake
to break the rules.

1788
02:49:00,004 --> 02:49:02,506
Forgive me.
- No, Chitti.

1789
02:49:03,174 --> 02:49:06,635
You learnt to break
rules from humans.

1790
02:49:06,636 --> 02:49:09,180
It's not just your mistake.

1791
02:49:10,181 --> 02:49:11,766
Thank you, doctor.

1792
02:49:16,979 --> 02:49:19,065
I am feeling good, doctor.

1793
02:49:39,377 --> 02:49:42,129
Be sure you're not
touching anything.

1794
02:49:43,339 --> 02:49:47,801
Children, you're looking at Chitti.

1795
02:49:47,802 --> 02:49:50,846
The most advanced
andro-humanized robot.

1796
02:49:51,222 --> 02:49:55,183
20 years ago, Dr.
Vaseegaran had built him.

1797
02:49:55,184 --> 02:49:58,854
And then it was
dismantled after a while.

1798
02:49:59,271 --> 02:50:00,523
Why?

1799
02:50:00,981 --> 02:50:02,608
I started thinking.

